{"tid":1581958,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有團體引述政府指考慮調整部分綜援措施","createTime":"2019-09-19T23:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T23:30:17.000Z","uid":219362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa3e42464090fb38c74533d543797d0809d9914","tid":1581958,"uid":219362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T23:30:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有關注綜援團體就收緊長者綜援年齡門檻安排約見勞福局局長羅致光。<br />\n<br />\n捍衛綜援權利大聯盟主動約見勞福局局長羅致光，要求政府全面檢討綜援制度及重新制定綜援標準金等。<br />\n<br />\n雙方會面超過一小時，他們會後引述羅致光透露會考慮調整部分綜援項目，包括上調租金津貼上限、增加對學童的支援措施等，但重申不會撤回收緊長者綜援年齡門檻的措施。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8C%87%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-123530129.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%2595%25B4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25B6%259C%25E6%258F%25B4%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD-123530129.html&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP6jPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=5d7efc86\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8C%87%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD-123530129.html</a>"}]}